* background "forest_bg.png"

Deep in the forest, you find an old shrine.
A mysterious figure stands guard.
* flush

* set metGuard, true
* set score, score + 20

* if score > 30
    The guardian seems impressed by your courage.
    * flush
* else
    The guardian eyes you suspiciously.
    * flush

* choice
    # Speak to the guardian
        The guardian whispers: "The path forward is yours to choose."
        * flush
        * goto_scene ending
    # Run away
        * goto_scene town
